{"tid":1892013,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打識用netgear router呀","createTime":"2020-02-22T09:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T16:13:54.000Z","uid":350570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f20033a4d5563b0965f576fb9e246ff6d52b9a8a","tid":1892013,"uid":350570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"我前2日買左netgear rax80啦<br />\n<br />\n咁屋企部電視呢我就係用lan線連router<br />\n<br />\n咁rax80有5個lan埠啦,我將電視條lan插落去lan5啦<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解lan5 led顯示係橙色,但係我部pc係連lan1, lan1 led係白色GE,<br />\n<br />\nrax80上面其他led都係著緊白色燈,係得lan5 led係橙色,<br />\n<br />\n咁我都有試下將電視條lan插其他lan埠, 都係會著橙色,<br />\n<br />\n電視可以正常上網ge,我上去管理個度睇,電視個狀態係寫住100M/全雙工<br />\n<br />\npc就係1000M/全雙工,我以為關條lan線事啦換左條cat6線比部電視,但係換左都係顯示100M/雙工,<br />\n<br />\n係咪部電視收唔到1000M所以連接埠會係橙色?望到係橙色硬係覺得好似有問題咁"},{"pid":"76d458576fad49fda5fcc70145ea6d771b6b7efb","tid":1892013,"uid":93599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"我router lan線出電視/switch都係橙燈<br />\n但使用又正常<br />\nr7000用家"},{"pid":"7fb114d7dd0c499aa57eca6a3105a593060aabe5","tid":1892013,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"電視拎到ip嗎？ router 睇到電視連接左嗎？電視肯定支援cat6 ma?"},{"pid":"ec7c8276bb0587504ce9584c58ceb58caf917718","tid":1892013,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"可能電視個lan port 得100M <br />\n睇返說明書 或者睇下電視個port隔離有無寫"},{"pid":"3bbfdfd01561bd871382e17a922f38a9dbf001e1","tid":1892013,"uid":241810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"第一件事 先update個firmware<br />\n<br />\n第二件事 reset成部router"},{"pid":"7b783a2e424cffe86a64b883f72dc0d141329ee5","tid":1892013,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"未開機冇連線掛<br />\n我用緊r6400 連PC PS4同電視<br />\n熄機個陣就會變橙燈 開機連網絡個陣就轉返白燈"},{"pid":"f266617699dcf6fb8bf6e2dad0c6c24425577e5e","tid":1892013,"uid":350570,"